      "description": "Dive into Marble Sort, the ultimate 3D physics puzzle that will test your logic, timing, and strategy!\n\nIn this vibrant and satisfying brain teaser, your goal is to sort falling marbles into their perfectly matched colored boxes. But there's a catch! Between the trays and the boxes lies a continuously moving circular conveyor belt.\n\nTap a tray to release the marbles and watch them drop with realistic physics onto the conveyor. As they travel around, they'll drop into the matching colored boxes at the bottom. Fill all 3 slots in a box to clear it! Be careful\u2014if marbles get stuck on the conveyor with no matching boxes available, it's game over.\n\nWhy You'll Love Marble Sort:\n\n-Dynamic Puzzle Mechanics: A unique blend of physics-based dropping and conveyor-belt strategy.\n-Satisfying Gameplay: The perfect mix of relaxing ASMR-style marble clinking and challenging brain-training.\n-Hundreds of Levels: Endless fun that scales in difficulty to keep your mind sharp!\n-Play Offline: Perfect for your commute. Enjoy the full game without WiFi or data.\n- Easy to Learn, Hard to Master: One-tap controls make it easy to play anywhere, anytime!\n\nStrategize your drops, clear the conveyor, and become the ultimate sorting master.\n\nDownload Marble Sort today and let the fun roll!",
